---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="SMS Privacy Policy | Water Heater Replacement Company"
	description="SMS Privacy Policy for the internal lead notification system used by Water Heater Replacement Company of Grand Rapids."
	robotsIndex={false}
	robotsFollow={false}
	showNavigation={false}
	showFooter={false}
>
	<main class="min-h-screen bg-white py-16 px-6">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <header class="mb-10 pb-8 border-b border-gray-200">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-gray-400 mb-3">Internal Use Only</p>
            <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-3">SMS Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Last Updated: June 30, 2026</p>
        </header>

        <div class="space-y-10 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
            We are committed to protecting the privacy of our internal team members, owners, and stakeholders. This Privacy Policy outlines the operational boundaries of our internal SMS notification system.
            </p>

            <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">1. No Collection of Personal Information</h2>
            <p>
                We do not collect any personal information, personal mobile numbers, or user data from recipients to operate this system. This notification loop utilizes only corporate endpoint numbers that are permanently assigned to company-provided assets and corporate roles. No user-submitted or consumer personal data is ever collected.
            </p>
            </section>

            <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">2. No Storage of Personal Data</h2>
            <p>
                Because this program functions strictly via hardcoded internal system configurations and corporate assets, we do not store personal contact information, personal text histories, or any private data within our backend systems for messaging purposes.
            </p>
            </section>

            <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">3. Strict Non-Sharing Clause</h2>
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">
                No mobile information will be shared with third parties or affiliates for marketing or promotional purposes. All the above categories exclude text messaging originator opt-in data and consent; this information will not be shared with any third parties.
            </p>
            </section>

            <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">4. Operational Boundaries</h2>
                <p>
                    This system is an automated, unidirectional pipeline designed strictly to push operational alerts to company stakeholders. It does not interface with external consumers, marketing funnels, or public-facing data tables.
                </p>
            </section>
        </div>
        </div>
	</main>
</BaseLayout>
